<!-- Game Controls Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">UNARMED COMBAT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Guard:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Left handed punch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Left</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Right handed punch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Kick:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Protect / Parry:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Down</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">CLUBS AND SIDE ARMS COMBAT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Guard:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Blow to the left:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Left</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Blow to the right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Frontal attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Protect / Parry:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Down</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">FIREARMS, MISSILES, PROJECTILES COMBAT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Aim:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn left to aim:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Left</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn right to aim:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire / Throw:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Reload:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad Down</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">OFFENSIVE MOVES CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Quick dodge to the left:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Quick dodge to the right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump forward:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Dodge backward:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">SEARCH / ACTION CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Search an area to earn a bonus, activate a mechanism, open a door or perform another action required by the situation (e.g., climb, lie face down:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">SELECT WEAPON CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Select next weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Previous weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">RAPID WEAPON EXCHANGE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Stores the current weapon and the previous weapon, so you can switch between the two quickly:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause / Unpause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>

      
