<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Hidden section -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">enter 'COMMANDO' in the password menu</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; All Weapons - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Triangle, Square, Circle, X, Triangle, Circle, Square, X, Triangle, Square, Triangle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Auto Recharge - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Square, X, Circle, Triangle, Circle, X, Square, Triangle, Circle, Triangle, Square.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Ammo - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Triangle, Circle, Triangle, X, Square, X, Circle, Square, Triangle, X, Square.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Level skip - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">X, Square, X, Triangle, Circle, Square, X, Circle, Triangle, Triangle.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Max Energy - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">X, Triangle, Triangle, Circle, X, Triangle, Triangle, Circle, Square, Circle, X.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Refill health - Pause the game, then highligh Sound FX, then enter the following -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">X, Triangle, Triangle, Circle, X, Triangle, Triangle, Circle, Square, Square, X.</font>&nbsp;<br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
